  "markup": "Review of the DLS Hands-Free Super Pulsed Laser system with Magna Cart. Ideal for treating the spine, knees, shoulders and other large muscle groups.\u0026nbsp; Allows you to treat multiple patients at once, and can increase ROI without increasing overhead."
